{"tid":683943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[俄佬攪局] 朝中社：俄羅斯外長將訪問朝鮮","createTime":"2018-05-30T06:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T08:58:38.000Z","uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9a6f2f6584e7b2272c7ae9773476511099c412","tid":683943,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:24:19.000Z","msg":"據朝中社的報道指出，朝鮮外長李容浩向拉夫羅夫提出訪問邀請，但該報道沒有交代有關訪問的時間或到訪原因。<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮領袖金正恩與美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）會面在即，雙方官員正着手商討會面細節。而金正恩亦在短期內兩度到訪中國，與中國國家主席習近平會面，當中第二次會面後，朝鮮態度突然180度轉變。<br />\n<br />\n假如拉夫羅夫在「特金會」前訪問平壤，或可能談及核問題，但未知他會否與金正恩見面。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國白宮發言人桑德斯（Sarah Sanders）周二（29日）表示，華府正積極籌備「特金會」，希望可以在下月12日如期舉行，但即使告吹，美國仍會為將來會面作準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/193711/朝中社-俄羅斯外長將訪問朝鮮\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F193711%2F%E6%9C%9D%E4%B8%AD%E7%A4%BE-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E5%B0%87%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE&d=5MiKebA02DEPhczAPv7l7ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=631c5b6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/193711/朝中社-俄羅斯外長將訪問朝鮮</a>"},{"pid":"f62f0c5fe5f795c4b1c106b9523c99a98a209152","tid":683943,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果中俄一齊撐金仔，金仔仲會唔會跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係中俄加埋俾到好多錢收買金仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acaac780b00ff1c125c82f2dac96acb10a2514b","tid":683943,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"一陣又180度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc346817d568ecdaf54f09882be89a88c238eb22","tid":683943,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc